for the next 48 hours.

248
00:19:59.156 --> 00:20:00.616
WILL: Deploying clockstopper!

249
00:20:00.699 --> 00:20:02.701
The Major will deploy
a magnetic clockstopper

250
00:20:02.784 --> 00:20:04.203
