251
00:20:04.286 --> 00:20:06.455
[he grunts and groans]

252
00:20:12.377 --> 00:20:15.172
[music intensifies]

253
00:20:17.841 --> 00:20:19.092
[grunts]
Oh fuck.

254
00:20:22.971 --> 00:20:24.723
Nobody fucking move!

255
00:20:24.806 --> 00:20:26.225
